{"tid":2423578,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"如果不是賭身家就不要浪費時間投資股票。","createTime":"2021-02-26T03:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T05:51:26.000Z","uid":60393,"like":53,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0365694bc6daa9d956394b2abf6eb613c522c701","tid":2423578,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"巴菲特向連登仔支付天價午餐時請教到的八大投資心得:<br />\n<br />\n1. 第1條投資原則是不要蝕錢，第2條原則是如果不是賭身家就不要浪費時間投資股票。 <br />\n<br />\n2. 投資的密訣是：別人「恐懼」時「借錢買牛」，別人「貪婪」時「借錢買熊」。<br />\n<br />\n4.把每項投資的股票都當作一樁生意是過時的觀念，應該要把股票當成雞來屌，屌完就離牠而去。<br />\n<br />\n5.風險來自於你沒有勇氣，不敢借貸。<br />\n<br />\n6.股票比債券更有吸引力，但牛熊才是成人的玩意。<br />\n<br />\n7. 長線投資是浪費人生，若你打算持有這隻股票達十年，則不要持有，直接去這間公司打工。<br />\n<br />\n8. 公司財報是沒有用的東西，百家樂的路紙更有參考價值。"},{"pid":"497abe8525212780d3e5746f8a042a03db87affc","tid":2423578,"uid":49302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8cf9ccb01a2f326a4420761d1865526313584b","tid":2423578,"uid":36739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e8167d37c209e4b6a69d24c5328f458ff72425","tid":2423578,"uid":327049,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h83f368.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh83f368.gif&h=8d83eae9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc22beca0daa91240264973b30d7ebb49d94386d","tid":2423578,"uid":285264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T04:17:33.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"8da6fb82efd1fcfd319ecee4e986239cbe095dc7","tid":2423578,"uid":147001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,